title: Can - (1995) The Peel Sessions [FLAC]
description:
Here it tis, the rare out of print CD by Can, The Peel Sessions.

With the astounding lineup of Michael Karoli, Irmin Schmidt, Holger Czukay, and Jaki Liebezeit (and Damo Suzuki on one track), this album is one of the more "normal" sounding Can albums that you&#039;ll hear.

This is a great album, and I&#039;m proud to share it here.

Enjoy!
